 </head>
 <body>
  <p>There should be a solid single uninterrupted smooth column of blue below.</p>
  <div class="a"> x </div>
  <div class="b"> x </div>
  <div class="c"> x </div>
  <div class="d"> x </div>
  <div class="e"> x </div>
  <div class="h"> x </div>
 </body>
</html>
